  "notes": "One track = one medley/mashup video. The songs strung together are the samples, IN ORDER. Structure is the troubadour splice: one continuous harmonic bed hosting sequential recognizable hooks. Timestamps are undocumented for this catalog (start_s/end_s null throughout). Track titles are the primary ground truth (verified via YouTube oembed and the artist's own site); song lists inside vaguely-named medleys come from search snippets / secondary write-ups and are marked in per-track note when order or membership is only partially confirmed. Two-song blends interleave rather than stack (opposite of Girl Talk collision). role is null unless a clear held-bed-vs-sung-hook distinction was documented. Durations for the 20 'This Is My Brain' tracks are from the artist's music page; standalone-video durations left null. YouTube watch-page and Invidious fetches were blocked (403/402) from this environment, so full video descriptions could not be scraped; oembed titles and web-search snippets were used instead.",
